com.tenforce.semtech.SPARQLParser.SPARQLStatements

Class BlockStatement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tenforce.semtech.SPARQLParser.SPARQLStatements.BlockStatement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IStatement
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UpdateBlockStatement, WhereBlockStatement

    public abstract class BlockStatement
extends java.lang.Object
implements IStatement
    Created by langens-jonathan on 20.07.16. version 0.0.1 Abstract class. The idea is that the update and where block types inherit from this block type because they allow for nested versions of each other. A block has a certain type, a graph upon which it operates and a list of statements between it's parentheses. The types of blocks are: - insert - delete - where - select
